Package agh.alleviation.presentation.context.manager

Class ServiceManager

java.lang.Object
agh.alleviation.presentation.context.manager.ServiceManager
@Component
public class ServiceManager
extends java.lang.Object
Provides logic and abstraction of Controller-Service-ObservableList communication. Introduced to decouple Controllers from Services and to allow showing the current database changes made in different parts of the application.
Author:
Anna Nosek
